### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080


### ─── Task 1: Core API ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a deposit
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### Create a transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount":   "ACC-67890",
  "amount":      250.75,
  "currency":    "USD",
  "type":        "transfer"
}a

###

### Create a withdrawal
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount":      50.00,
  "currency":    "EUR",
  "type":        "withdrawal"
}

###

### List all transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

###

### Get transaction by ID  (replace <id> with an actual UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/<id>

###

### Get account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

###

### Get account balance (receiver)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-67890/balance


### ─── Task 3: Filtering ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Filter by account
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

###

### Filter by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=transfer

###

### Filter by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

###

### Combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=transfer&from=2024-01-01


### ─── Task 4: CSV Export ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Export all transactions as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=csv


### ─── Task 2: Validation errors ──────────────────────────────────

### Invalid amount (negative)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount":   "ACC-67890",
  "amount":      -50.00,
  "currency":    "USD",
  "type":        "transfer"
}

###

### Invalid account format
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "BADFORMAT",
  "toAccount":   "ACC-67890",
  "amount":      100.00,
  "currency":    "USD",
  "type":        "transfer"
}

###

### Invalid currency
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount":   "ACC-67890",
  "amount":      100.00,
  "currency":    "XYZ",
  "type":        "transfer"
}
